              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3689630617829598800">A fictionalized account of the proto-history of Indian sub-continent. It foresees a Greek attack before The attack by Alaxander.. Kala writes with aplomb, giving us a pee kinto the lives, customs and the wars of the people of Sapta Sindhu and their relations with the people of Arianna. <br/>A must read to know how we have evolved as a nation...<br/>HIGHLY RECOMMENDED..</span>

          </span>
        </div>


