  <span id="freeText17718000666405421754" style="display:none">My first read this year. Took a really long time as it is my first read on Kindle. (How I wish it has a paper back)!<br />A wonderful historical thriller. It is one of those book which delves deep into the history of Central &amp; west Asia. The fictional story is all about politics and religion. This book is different from the other books I read and loved it. What surprised me the most is the so-called present day rogue countries where war is their everyday life once spoke of peace and were highly civilised nations once upon a time. Highly Recommended.</span>
